  "keyFeatures": [
    "Pattern-based code search across 30+ languages",
    "Semantic pattern matching with metavariables and ellipsis operators",
    "SAST, SCA (Supply Chain), and Secrets scanning",
    "Taint analysis for data-flow tracking",
    "Autofix support for automated code remediation",
    "CI/CD integration (GitHub, GitLab, CircleCI)",
    "MCP server for AI coding assistant integration",
    "Rule registry with 2,000+ community-driven rules",
